						               													<description>NooPolitik is a non-collectable table- top card game designed by Ben Drain and published through the print-on-demand site thegamecrafter.com . &amp;#10;Players take on the role of one of 12 countries attempting to make a mark on history. As such, the theme of the game is historical and political. Players interact with each other through the spheres of political, military, clandestine, and economic pools of resources, using 3 different bidding systems. When a player accomplishes a feat such as bringing a new achievement into the world, or expunging someone else&amp;rsquo;s, they score a card towards victory, playing to 21 points.&amp;#10;The game contains 12 unique country cards, 96 unique action cards, 104 unique achievements, 18 multicolored non-standard dice, and a large collection of resource tokens  representing the resources of the game (labor, steel, plastics, unrest, etc), and 50 glass beads used for bidding.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
